Booking Confirmed!

Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,

Your tee time at <%= @course.name %> has been confirmed.

Booking Details:
- Date: <%= @tee_time.date.strftime('%A, %B %d, %Y') %>
- Tee Time: <%= @tee_time.formatted_time %>
- Players: <%= @booking.players_count %>
- Confirmation Code: <%= @booking.confirmation_code %>
<% if @booking.total_cents.to_i > 0 %>- Total: <%= @booking.total.format %><% end %>

<% if @booking.booking_players.any? %>
Players in your group:
<% @booking.booking_players.each do |player| %>- <%= player.name %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

Please arrive at least 15 minutes before your tee time.

<%= @organization.name %>
